petual and spot prices. The exchange uses a time-weighted average price (TWAP) methodology during the final hour before settlement. Portfolio margin mode allows cross-collateralization with other positions, reducing margin requirements. Funding payments occur at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC, with rates typically ranging from -0.375% to +0.375% daily."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
